original_title: Rik Emmett - One Night in Cinci
overview: Rik Emmett's “One Night In Cinci” was filmed LIVE at the 20th Century Theatre in Cincinnati, OH on August 6th, 2004.  This short 8-song set was performed as a duo with Marty Anderson on keyboards and background vocals. It includes many of Rik’s popular acoustic songs from “Good Faith,” “Handiwork,” and more!
title: Rik Emmett - One Night in Cinci
